NAMING_CONVENTION:
The codebase uses lowercase_underscore naming for commodities:
- organics (not BASIC_FOOD) - Database columns, all services, all frontend
- equipment (not TECHNOLOGY) - Database columns, all services, all frontend
- colonists (not POPULATION) - Database columns, all services, all frontend
The ResourceType enum in resource.py uses UPPER_CASE names but is largely unused in trading flows.
See /DOCS/STATUS/COMMODITY_NAMING_ANALYSIS.md for detailed analysis.

